    <detaileddescription>
<para>The <ref refid="classBluetoothLowEnergyReceiver" kindref="compound">BluetoothLowEnergyReceiver</ref> connects to a BLE device and feeds the QgsNmeaConnection over a proxy QIODevice using QLowEnergyController. It receives QgsGpsInformation and converts it to <ref refid="classGnssPositionInformation" kindref="compound">GnssPositionInformation</ref> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
